South Africa Minister’s Wife Is Imprisoned for Dealing Drugs, Sapa Reports

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-05-06T10:23:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/south-africa-minister-s-wife-imprisoned-for-drug-dealing-sapa-reports.html
(Corrects spelling of Pietermaritzburg.)  Sheryl Cwele, the wife of  South
Africa ’s security minister, has been sentenced to 12 years in
prison for drug dealing by the Pietermaritzburg High Court, the
South African Press Association reported today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at   asguazzin@bloomberg.net  